      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> halloumi slices </strong>to a baking tray</p><p>Drizzle with <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and sprinkle over the <strong>smoked paprika</strong></p><p>Put the tray directly under the grill for 4-5 min or until warmed through and softened – this is your <strong>smoky halloumi</strong></p>",
